Class ElementMapping

java.lang.Object
  org.productivity.java.habitat4j.compat.common.ElementMapping
public class ElementMapping
extends java.lang.Object

ElementMapping is an object that defines the "target" information relating to XML elements used by AbstractXMLMap.
